com.microsoft.azure.management.network

Interface VirtualNetworkGatewayOperations

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    VirtualNetworkGatewayOperationsImpl

    public interface VirtualNetworkGatewayOperations
    The Network Resource Provider API includes operations for managing the Virtual network Gateway for your subscription.
